PrecisAmendment to the MEDICAL DEVICES REGULATIONS permitting a practitioner to apply to the Health Protection Branch for the issuance, on compassionate grounds, of a letter authorizing the sale of a device that could not otherwise be sold in Canada because it does not meet all applicable regulatory requirements.
